		"description": "<p>During a Safe Rest, brew INT+WIL Concoctions in your cauldron. Action: You may drink a Concoction or throw it as a ranged attack (Reach 6). The target gains the Concoction's effect. Unused Concoctions expire after your next Safe Rest.</p><hr><p><strong>Concoction Effects</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Minor Health.</strong> Gain 2×KEY temp HP.</li><li><strong>Fitness.</strong> Gain +1 STR &amp; +1 DEX for 1 minute.</li><li><strong>Speed.</strong> Gain +6 Speed for 1 minute.</li><li><strong>Minor Cure.</strong> End any single harmful condition.</li><li><strong>Delayed Action.</strong> Gain one extra Action at the end of your turn.</li><li><strong>Crackling.</strong> Gain the Charged condition.</li><li><strong>Smoke.</strong> Gain the Invisible condition until the start of your next turn.</li><li><strong>Affliction.</strong> Apply one Affliction you know.</li></ul>",
